title: Flight Simulator 2020 - MSFS Update - Aircraft & Avionics Update 1 - released
description:
In this video we will go through the changes which are part of the 1st Aircraft & Avionics Update (AAU) which has been released earlier today. With this update it is critical to remove the Working Title versions of the avionics systems because they are now native build in MSFS and could conflict with eachother.,
